    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>Approximately 50 posters and other ephemera representing leaders and heroes of the Indian subcontinent.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite audience="internal" id="aspace_8e1816ded647a28fcff9117f5f128d7c">
